OL,6,FA museum struggling to "keep the
OL,7,Flights on" due to soaring energy bills
OL,8,Fhas appealed to the public for help.
OL,10,FMuseum has issued an plea to the
OL,11,Fpublic to help raise money to
OL,12,Fsafeguard the site's future.
OL,14,FThe museum says that the rising has
OL,15,Fmeant it's struggling to keep up with
OL,16,Fcosts, and could be forced to close.
OL,18,FThe is an independent charity which
OL,19,Fsurvives on grant funding but says its
OL,20,Fcosts have quadrupled, and this no
OL,21,Flonger stretches far enough.
