OL,3,CMuseum struggling to 'keep the lights
OL,4,Con' due to 'astronomic' energy bills
OL,6,FDirector Dawn Lancaster said: "It is
OL,7,Fdefinitely a threat because at the
OL,8,Fmoment our energy bills are in the
OL,9,Fregion of #35,000 a year, which is
OL,10,Fastronomic.
OL,12,F"We can't turn everything off because
OL,13,Fwe have to have stable conditions to
OL,14,Fmaintain the artefacts in the
OL,15,Fbuilding."
OL,17,FThe museum is home to around 9,000
OL,18,Fartefacts.
