OL,6,FShe said if the museum is forced to
OL,7,Fclose, the exhibits would
OL,8,F"deteriorate" and could be "lost
OL,9,Fentirely to the people of this county."
OL,11,FPatrick Cunningham, a volunteer, said
OL,12,F"this is the only place like this in
OL,13,FLlandudno" and if it closed it would
OL,14,F"leave a hole".
OL,16,F"This is a facility for Llandudno that
OL,17,Fis irreplaceable," he said. "Once it
OL,18,Fis lost it's gone forever."
